---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for ChefBouyon and Scaling Legends applications.">
  <main style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; color: #e0e0e0;">
    <h1 style="color: #e94560; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p style="color: #888; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Last updated: March 14, 2026</p>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">1. Introduction</h2>
      <p>This Privacy Policy describes how ChefBouyon and Scaling Legends ("we", "us", or "our") collect, use, and share information in connection with our applications, websites, and services, including our use of the Meta (Facebook/Instagram) platform.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>When you interact with our services or advertisements, we may collect:</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li>Basic profile information provided by Meta (name, profile picture, email address) when you authorize our application</li>
        <li>Interaction data such as clicks, page views, and conversions through the Meta Pixel</li>
        <li>Device and browser information for analytics and ad optimization</li>
        <li>Any information you voluntarily provide to us</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use collected information to:</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li>Deliver and optimize advertising campaigns on Meta platforms</li>
        <li>Measure the effectiveness of our marketing efforts</li>
        <li>Build custom and lookalike audiences for ad targeting</li>
        <li>Improve our services and user experience</li>
        <li>Communicate with you when you reach out to us</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">4. Meta Platform Data</h2>
      <p>Our use of information received from Meta APIs adheres to the <a href="https://developers.facebook.com/terms/" style="color: #e94560;">Meta Platform Terms</a> and <a href="https://developers.facebook.com/policy/" style="color: #e94560;">Developer Policies</a>. We do not sell data obtained from Meta. We only use Meta platform data for the purposes described in this policy and as permitted by Meta's terms.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">5. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share data with:</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li>Meta/Facebook for ad delivery and measurement purposes</li>
        <li>Analytics providers to help us understand service usage</li>
        <li>Service providers who assist in operating our services</li>
        <li>Law enforcement when required by law</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain personal data only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy. Ad interaction data is typically retained for up to 180 days for optimization purposes.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
        <li>Opt out of targeted advertising through your Meta ad preferences</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">8. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p>We use the Meta Pixel and similar technologies to track conversions and optimize ad delivery. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings and Meta's <a href="https://www.facebook.com/help/568137493302217" style="color: #e94560;">ad preferences</a>.</p>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      <h2 style="color: #fff;">9. Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related questions or data requests, contact us at: <a href="mailto:chiefbala@gmail.com" style="color: #e94560;">chiefbala@gmail.com</a></p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
